title: Palestine Labor Force Participation Rate
description: Labor Force Participation Rate in Palestine increased to 46 percent in the third quarter of 2022 from 44 percent in the second quarter of 2022. Labor Force Participation Rate in Palestine averaged 44.08 percent from 2009 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 47.10 percent in the fourth quarter of 2018 and a record low of 38.60 percent in the second quarter of 2020. This page provides - Palestine Labor Force Participation Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics
